---
import AboutHeroImage from "../assets/blog-placeholder-about.jpg";
import Layout from "../../layouts/AboutCV.astro";
import Button from "../../components/Button.astro";
---

<Layout title="Sobre mi">
  <section class="cv-about">
    <p>
      I’m <b>Alberto Pascual</b>, and I go beyond the role of <b
        >Senior Backend Engineer</b
      >. With more than <b>10 years of experience</b> designing and building <b
        >scalable solutions</b
      >, I bring a vision that combines <b>backend architecture</b>, <b
        >cost efficiency</b
      >, and <b>DevOps culture</b>, always aiming for technology to deliver
      <b>true value</b>.
    </p>
    <p>
      I’ve had the opportunity to work with great people in teams of all sizes
      at companies such as <b>SEAT:CODE</b>, <b>INCOM</b>, <b>BLOOCK</b>, and <b
        >DEXMA</b
      >. At <b>SEAT:CODE</b>, I contributed to product improvement by
      implementing
      <b>distributed caching</b> and migrating towards a more <b
        >efficient service-oriented architecture</b
      >. At <b>VERYCHIC</b>, I promoted <b>engineering best practices</b> by applying
      <b>SOLID principles</b> and <b>Clean Architecture</b>, strengthening both
      <b>quality</b> and <b>software maintainability</b>.
    </p>
    <p>
      My profile combines the <b>technical</b> with the <b>personal</b>: a <b
        >curious reader</b
      >, an <b>amateur pianist</b>, and above all, someone passionate about <b
        >solving complex challenges</b
      >
      that go beyond <b>known limits</b>, always seeking <b>new perspectives</b>
      and <b>creative solutions</b>.
    </p>
  </section>
  <div class="cv-download-top">
    <Button
      href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/download/resume.pdf`}
      class="about-cta">Descargar CV</Button
    >
  </div>
  <section class="timeline">
    <div class="timeline-item left">
      <span class="date">SSE <- [ Dec 2021 ]</span>
      <div class="content">
        <h3>SEAT:CODE</h3>
        <p>
          Backend architecture design, cost control, and continuous improvement,
          with cross-team collaboration.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="timeline-item right">
      <span class="date">[ Mar 2022 - May 2024 ] -> Technical Lead</span>
      <div class="content">
        <h3>INCOM</h3>
        <p>
          Built the platform and APIs from scratch, integrated payment systems,
          and implemented cost control, with full responsibility for backend and
          infrastructure.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="timeline-item left">
      <span class="date">Lead Engineer <- [ Sep 2021 - Dec 2021 ]</span>
      <div class="content">
        <h3>BLOOCK</h3>
        <p>
          API integration and improvement in blockchain solutions, while
          mentoring a fast-growing team.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="timeline-item right">
      <span class="date">[ Oct 2020 - Sept 2021 ] -> SSE</span>
      <div class="content">
        <h3>Dexma</h3>
        <p>
          Ensured platform stability, developed real-time ingestion pipelines,
          and implemented IoT integrations.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="timeline-item left">
      <span class="date">Backend Engineer <- [ Jan 2018 - Oct 2020 ]</span>
      <div class="content">
        <h3>VERYCHIC</h3>
        <p>
          Developed APIs, batch processes, and AWS Lambdas, applying SOLID
          principles and Hexagonal Architecture.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="timeline-item right">
      <span class="date">[ Sep 2014 - Jan 2018 ] -> Software Developer</span>
      <div class="content">
        <h3>GFI Spain</h3>
        <p>
          Delivered projects for multiple clients in a technology consultancy
          environment.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="cv-download-bottom">
    <Button
      href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/download/resume.pdf`}
      class="about-cta">Download CV</Button
    >
  </div>

  <section class="languages">
    <h2>- Languages</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><b>Spanish:</b> native</li>
      <li><b>Catalan:</b> father tongue</li>
      <li><b>English:</b> intermediate level (in progress)</li>
    </ul>
  </section>
  <section class="education">
    <h2>- Education</h2>
    <div class="edu-item">
      <h3>INSTITUT OBERT DE CATALUNYA (IOC)</h3>
      <span class="date">2013</span>
      <p>Higher Technician in Multiplatform Application Development.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="edu-item">
      <h3>UNIVERSITAT OBERTA DE CATALUNYA (UOC)</h3>
      <span class="date">Present</span>
      <p>
        Currently pursuing a degree in Computer Engineering. I especially enjoy
        the practical approach and flexibility of the UOC, which allows me to
        dive deeper into topics I am passionate about and connect theory with
        professional practice.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <style>
    .cv-about {
      border-bottom: 2px solid #444;
    }

    .cv-about b {
      color: var(--font-color-normal);
    }
    .timeline {
      position: relative;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .timeline::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      bottom: 0;
      left: 50%;
      width: 3px;
      background: var(--boder-color);
      transform: translateX(-50%);
    }

    .timeline-item {
      position: relative;
      width: 405px;
      padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
    }

    .timeline-item::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      top: 1.2rem;
      width: 16px;
      height: 16px;
      background: var(--background);
      border: 3px solid var(--boder-color);
      border-radius: 50%;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .timeline-item.left {
      text-align: right;
      left: 0;
    }

    .timeline-item.left p {
      left: 0;
      text-align: left;
    }

    .timeline-item.left::before {
      right: -11px;
    }

    .timeline-item.right {
      left: 50%;
    }

    .timeline-item.right::before {
      left: -11px;
    }

    .content {
      background: var(--background-highlight);
      color: var(--font-color-normal);
      padding: 0.5rem;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px var(--box-shadow);
      font-size: 0.8rem;
    }

    .content h3 {
      margin: 0;
    }

    .left {
      margin: 0;
    }

    .date {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: var(--font-color-normal);
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      margin-top: 0.4rem;
    }

    .timeline-item:hover .content {
      background-color: var(--background-hover);
    }
    .timeline-item:hover::before {
      background: var(--background-hover);
    }

    .cv-download-top {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 1rem;
    }

    .cv-download-bottom {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .education,
    .languages {
      color: var(--font-color-normal);
    }

    .education h2,
    .languages h2 {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      border-bottom: 2px solid var(--boder-color);
      padding-bottom: 0.3rem;
      padding-top: 3rem;
    }

    .edu-item {
      margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
    }

    .edu-item p {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
    }

    .edu-item h3 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: var(--font-color-highlight);
    }

    .edu-item .date {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: var(--font-color-normal);
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
    }

    .languages ul {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
    }

    .languages li {
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      color: var(--font-color-normal);
    }
    .languages li b {
      color: var(--font-color-highlight);
    }
  </style>
</Layout>
